00164 /*   of ephemeral symbols, floats, and integers.          */
00165 /*                                                        */
00166 /*   associatedValue: Contains a pointer to the storage   */
00167 /*   structure for the symbol, float, or integer which is */
00168 /*   ephemeral.                                           */

00171 /*   in a list of ephemeral items.                        */
